<A>__{ominous, threatening music. the upper tail fin of a jet plane emerges through the cloud layer and passes through the frame like a shark's fin through water. it passes by again in the opposite direction. music builds as the fin comes straight toward the camera, music swells to crescendo as entire jet plane lifts out of clouds and passes overhead. title slashes across screen, "airplane!" credits and music continue over following.}
